History

Version: 0.9
Release date: 2010-09-25 Velocity Tint

Translate note velocity into key pressed color tint
Custom note names

Version: 0.8
Release date: 2009-09-23 Raw & Black Keys

Raw keyboard events support.
SVG graphics giving black keys a nice 3D effect.

Version: 0.7
Release date: 2009-08-02 Note names

New properties: showLabels, useFlats and transpose.

Version: 0.6
Release date: 2008-10-05 Reasonable limits

minNote and maxNote properties to limit the note numbers.
selectedColor property renamed to keyPressedColor
keyboardMap fixes, mouse handling enhanced.

Version: 0.5
Release date: 2008-09-05 Hash smoke

Speed optimisation and fixes

Version: 0.4
Release date: 2008-08-10 Fashion keys

Version: 0.3
Release date: 2008-07-20 New rotation property

The new property allows to change, while working in the designer, the
rotation of the keyboard to show it vertical, or with any angle. 

Version: 0.2
Release date: 2008-07-13 Bug fixed

Version: 0.1 
Release date: 2008-07-12 Initial release

This component requires at least Qt 4.3 

To compile, using a command line shell change to the directory where you 
unpacked the sources and enter the command:

    $ qmake

followed by:

    $ make

To install the plugin for QtDesigner:

(in Linux)
    $ sudo make install
(in windows)
    > make install
    
To uninstall:

(in Linux)
    $ sudo make uninstall
(in windows)
    > make uninstall

To try the demo program without needing to install it, after a successful 
compilation do:

(in linux)
    $ sh vpiano.sh
(in windows)
    > vpiano.bat

Enjoy!
